archimate:ArchimateDiagramModel.documentation: https://www.hosiaisluoma.fi/blog/archimate-metamodel/ Service: Outside (Blackbox) Whitebox (inside view) - Process: behaviour with start and end (digestive process) - Function: continuous behaviour (oxygen blood heart/lung function) https://archimate-community.pages.opengroup.org/workgroups/archimate-101/#_the_generic_metamodel_and_the_system_metaphor

children.content: The relation from “Node” to “Application Component” can be either “serving” or “realization” (according to derivation rules) These elements can be applied to most of the modelling cases (80%), added with relation type “Flow” (between actors, processes and applications).
